text: Kerstin Rehders (born 18 November 1962) is a German rower. She competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dormagen
